<span face="" style="background-color: white; color: #111111;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">Beantown Web has developed such a system.&nbsp; For the ninth year running Beantown Web has conducted a quasi-scientific meta-search to identify the best business books published during the calendar year. These books are most likely to add value to your career.
</span>

<br />
<br />

<span style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">This year's search began by identifying 11 "Best of" lists. This resource list is available upon request. Presented here are the results.
</span>

<br />
<br />

</span>

<div style="background-color: white;">
<span style="color: #111111; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">A total of 110 books were mentioned on at least one "Best of" list -- 77 of these books were mentioned only once.
